{"id": "art-2721", "label": "Art. 2721", "title": "Art. 2721", "slug": "art-2721", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_34899533\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1083\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_34899533\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 272<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2116062818\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1082\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2116062818\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>Se <span class=SpellE>pedepse&#351;te</span> cu închisoare\nde la un an la 5 ani fondatorul, administratorul, directorul general,\ndirectorul, membrul consiliului de supraveghere sau al directoratului ori reprezentantul\nlegal al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> care:</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_284643609\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1081\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_284643609\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)<span class=SpellE>r&#259;spânde&#351;te</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;tiri</span> false sau <span class=SpellE>întrebuin&#355;eaz&#259;</span>\nalte mijloace frauduloase care au ca efect m&#259;rirea ori sc&#259;derea\nvalorii <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span> sau a <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iunilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> ori a altor titluri ce îi <span\nclass=SpellE>apar&#355;in</span>, în scopul <span class=SpellE>ob&#355;inerii</span>,\npentru el sau pentru alte persoane, a unui folos în paguba <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2083495268\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1080\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2083495268\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)încaseaz&#259; sau <span class=SpellE>pl&#259;te&#351;te</span>\ndividende, sub orice form&#259;, din profituri fictive ori care nu puteau fi\ndistribuite în cursul <span class=SpellE>exerci&#355;iului</span> financiar pe\nbaza <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iei</span> financiare interimare <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> anual, pe baza <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iilor</span>\nfinanciare anuale, sau contrar celor rezultate din acestea.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}